" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MessageEvent\"><code>MessageEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/MessagePort\"><code>MessagePort</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Navigator\"><code>Navigator</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PageTransitionEvent\"><code>PageTransitionEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Plugin\"><code>Plugin</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PluginArray\"><code>PluginArray</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PopStateEvent\"><code>PopStateEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PromiseRejectionEvent\"><code>PromiseRejectionEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RadioNodeList\"><code>RadioNodeList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/ValidityState\"><code>ValidityState</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>O&nbsp;<strong><code>HTMLElement.offsetLeft</code></strong>&nbsp;é um método apenas&nbsp;de leitura que retorna a medida, em&nbsp;pixels, da distância do canto superior esquerdo do elemento atual para o nó&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/offsetParent\"><code>HTMLElement.offsetParent</code></a>.</p>\n\n<p>Para elementos \"block-level\", que ocupam todo o espaço do elemento pai, o&nbsp;<code>offsetTop</code>, <code>offsetLeft</code>, <code>offsetWidth</code>, e <code>offsetHeight</code> representam a borda de um elemento relativo ao&nbsp;<code>offsetParent</code>.</p>\n\n<p>Entretando,&nbsp;para elementos \"inline-level\" &nbsp;(como o&nbsp;<strong>span</strong>) que podem&nbsp;envolver de uma linha para outra, o&nbsp;<code>offsetTop</code>&nbsp;e&nbsp;<code>offsetLeft</code> representam a posição da primeira borda&nbsp;(use <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/getClientRects\"><code>Element.getClientRects()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> para retornar a largura e altura), enquanto&nbsp;<code>offsetWidth</code> e <code>offsetHeight</code>&nbsp;representam as dimensões&nbsp;do bloco delimitador&nbsp;(use <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Element/getBoundingClientRect\"><code>Element.getBoundingClientRect()</code></a> pra retornar sua posição).&nbsp;Portanto, um bloco que possua um&nbsp;left, top, widht ou&nbsp;height do&nbsp;<code>offsetLeft, offsetTop, offsetWidth</code> e <code>offsetHeight</code> não será um delimitador para um&nbsp;span com texto envolvido.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Sintaxe","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"eval notranslate\"><em>left</em> = <em>element</em>.offsetLeft;\n</pre>\n\n<p><code>left</code> é um número inteiro representando o deslocamento para esquerda, em pixels,&nbsp;&nbsp;do elemento pai mais próximo posicionado com relative.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"Exemplo","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">var colorTable = document.getElementById(\"t1\");\nvar tOLeft = colorTable.offsetLeft;\n\nif (tOLeft &gt; 5) {\n  // deslocamento à esquerda maior que 5: faça alguma coisa\n}\n</pre>\n\n<p>Esse exemplo mostra uma frase&nbsp;'longa' envolvida por uma div com uma borda azul, e uma caixa vermelha que deveria delimitar o span.</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"Image:offsetLeft.jpg\" class=\"internal\" src=\"/@api/deki/files/790/=OffsetLeft.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">&lt;div style=\"width: 300px; border-color:blue;\n  border-style:solid; border-width:1;\"&gt;\n  &lt;span&gt;Short span. &lt;/span&gt;\n  &lt;span id=\"long\"&gt;Long span that wraps within this div.&lt;/span&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n\n&lt;div id=\"box\" style=\"position: absolute; border-color: red;\n  border-width: 1; border-style: solid; z-index: 10\"&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n\n&lt;script&gt;\n  var box = document.getElementById(\"box\");\n  var long = document.getElementById(\"long\");\n  box.style.left = long.offsetLeft + document.body.scrollLeft + \"px\";\n  box.style.top = long.offsetTop + document.body.scrollTop + \"px\";\n  box.style.width = long.offsetWidth + \"px\";\n  box.style.height = long.offsetHeight<span style=\"line-height: normal;\"> + \"px\"</span><span style=\"line-height: normal;\">;\n</span><span style=\"line-height: normal;\">&lt;/script&gt; </span></pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specification","title":"Especificação","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Especificação</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comentário</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/cssom-view/#dom-htmlelement-offsetleft\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Object Model (CSSOM) View Module<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'offsetLeft' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">Rascunho atual</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect2\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect3\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari (WebKit)</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte Básico</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Android Webview</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Firefox OS</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n   <th>Chrome para Android</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte Básico</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<p>Em conformidade com a especificação, essa propriedade &nbsp;retornará&nbsp;<code>null no</code>&nbsp;Webkit se o elemento não estiver sendo exibido (o <code>style.display</code> desse elemento ou ancestral estiver como&nbsp;<code>\"none\"</code>) ou se o&nbsp;<code>style.position</code> do elemento estiver setado como&nbsp;<code>\"fixed\"</code>.</p>\n\n<p>Essa propriedade retornará&nbsp;<code>null</code> no Internet Explorer (9) se o&nbsp;<code>style.position</code> do elemento estiver setado como <code>\"fixed\"</code>. (Ter&nbsp;<code>display:none</code> não afeta esse browser.)</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"Veja também","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/offsetParent\"><code>HTMLElement.offsetParent</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/offsetTop\"><code>HTMLElement.offsetTop</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/offsetWidth\"><code>HTMLElement.offsetWidth</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/offsetHeight\"><code>HTMLElement.offsetHeight</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Sintaxe","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Exemplo","id":"example"},{"text":"Especificação","id":"specification"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"Veja também","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"O HTMLElement.offsetLeft é um método apenas de leitura que retorna a medida, em pixels, da distância do canto superior esquerdo do elemento atual para o nó HTMLElement.offsetParent.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"HTMLElement.offsetLeft","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"HTMLElement.offsetLeft","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"element.offsetLeft","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"HTMLElement.offsetLeft","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"element.offsetLeft","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"HTMLElement.offsetLeft","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"HTMLElement.offsetLeft","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/api/htmlelement/offsetleft","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/api/htmlelement/offsetleft/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API","title":"APIs da Web"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement","title":"HTMLElement"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/offsetLeft","title":"HTMLElement.offsetLeft"}],"pageTitle":"HTMLElement.offsetLeft - APIs da Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}